{{wikipedia}}
==English==

===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɑː(r)k|-ɑː(r)k]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{zoology}} a scaleless [[fish]] with a cartilagenous [[skeleton]] that has 5 to 7 gill slits on each side of its head
# {{sports}} a person who [[feign]]s [[ineptitude]] to win money from others, as in "pool shark"
# ''(derisive, colloquial):'' a ([[sleazy]]) [[lawyer]]; an [[ambulance chaser]]

